    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Emberfall</strong> 是第一个 Roguevania-Survivor：一款融合了 Roguelite、Metroidvania 和生存元素的动作平台游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >穿越倒塌的城市“Lemia”的危险地下墓道，充满了危险和神秘，在10分钟内逃脱——否则将面临永恒的厄运。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Emberfall 让你操控 Kali，她曾击败了贪婪之神和光明女神。现在，诸神已经失败，城市将会坍塌。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏快速且具有挑战性，控制简单且充满无尽的挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301890/extras/19639874b637bebadd7097828ccab903.poster.avif?t=1749048123\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301890/extras/19639874b637bebadd7097828ccab903.webm?t=1749048123\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301890/extras/19639874b637bebadd7097828ccab903.mp4?t=1749048123\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >享受一个休闲战斗系统，专注于寻找出口，同时躲避敌人并磨练你的技能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你必须解锁某些技能才能进展。就像 Metroidvania 游戏，但没有复杂的进程和世界地图。只需享受短暂的游戏过程：<strong>玩、死、学、重复。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301890/extras/0b18b2baabd5e923cda0ad41ab6931f9.avif?t=1749048123\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301890/extras_big/0b18b2baabd5e923cda0ad41ab6931f9.avif?t=1749048123 width=800 height=450 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏提供了一个简单的 <strong>Roguelite 系统</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在你的每次游戏过程中购买升级，使你在下一次游戏中变得更强大。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301890/extras/1082eeefc63bbc8f19a7e0a1d3f5a360.avif?t=1749048123\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301890/extras_big/1082eeefc63bbc8f19a7e0a1d3f5a360.avif?t=1749048123 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >开发者的开始提示：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >经验点自动收集，所以不要害怕逃跑。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >观察你的攻击条，并瞄准怪物群；你的攻击是全方位有效的。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在游戏开始时，提升你的攻击速度或解锁新的攻击法术，而不是集中于伤害。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在商店消费你的钱，将帮助你在未来的游戏中更顺利。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >一款由社区帮助开发和改进的游戏</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与我分享你的想法、建议、改进和反馈，帮助我改善这款游戏！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >社区欢迎所有人加入 Steam Hub 或 Discord。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有不好的体验或遇到BUG吗？请通过帖子告诉我（即使是负面反馈），而不是发布负面评论，这样我可以改善游戏！</p>",
